Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.96,0:00:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.58,0:00:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 姆伽罗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 姆伽罗就是姆伽罗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿萨谢尔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请助我一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很想救恶魔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请帮帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从斗技场逃跑的几人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今仍在逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为防他们逃离王都
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.71,0:00:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已布下严密的包围网
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协助逃跑的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是法瓦罗?雷欧涅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会一并解决掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.09,0:00:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有红龙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我们一定会解决它的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有他们的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红龙也出现过数次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要追下去想必早晚能遇上的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦发现 就地杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.53,0:01:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红龙有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.29,0:01:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.51,0:01:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么放跑他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.47,0:01:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.34,0:01:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你在竟然还出这么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今失去艾尔意昧着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我立刻动身搜查艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.52,0:01:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.98,0:01:52.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要把艾尔带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他如果被人类抓住 会被杀掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能眼睁睁看着他去死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就算去了 也只是累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言 既然艾尔不信任你们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你们去了也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只有一人我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.55,0:02:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.30,0:02:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.28,0:02:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真够惨的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.79,0:02:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会以为这样就算乔装了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:02:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿萨谢尔去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 早上人就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次不会炸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.38,0:04:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道？你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:04:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还活着啊 师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是师傅 无敌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 看来你也一样啊 唯独狗屎运过人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这表情啥意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…你看我就没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥见到凯撒就脸红了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉很久没像这样闹过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好想喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个少年是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在神界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是凯撒?利德法尔德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原先是你妈妈的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才多久没见 就变拽了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.56,0:06:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想查清
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏利欧斯王接下来打算干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.07,0:06:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王在先前的战斗中使用的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那破坏力太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要王有意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与十年前相当的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会再度降临在世上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要没那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能让人类走回正道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭我的力量能办到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢 你个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确 只要能封印那个兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论王的意图是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都能阻止破坏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手镯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？手镯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见王驱动那个黑球时的场景了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个手镯有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抢走那个手镯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽罗 你要是违背我们的约定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 先搜集情报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果夏利欧斯正在酝酿巨大的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我们来阻止他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家助我一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我跟着还出了这种事 真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他跑了是一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草率解放了他的力量也是一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们太性急了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们被艾尔的力量冲昏了头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果忘了他的精神还不足以驾驭这股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.09,0:07:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想失去恩人艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:08:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我衷心希望 能立刻将他从人间带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再让他一直陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 搜查的任务就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你一定会救我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我一起去人间找艾尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们母子救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次该你为我们母子贡献力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,索菲大人 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在人间 你是被通缉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切记不要轻易做出危险的举动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能发誓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这下我就跟巴卡斯一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.47,0:09:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟真的恶魔一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:05.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去搜集情报咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜小姐兴奋地冲出去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她出去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙无忧无虑的 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是跟去看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓？为啥要我去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是她师傅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有毛关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去 爆炸头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.25,0:10:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天晓得小妹妹会被卷入什么纠纷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给你了 法瓦罗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔找我有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是谁的墓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我母亲的墓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:11:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何这么吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才…才没吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为平民却成了王的侧室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚怀上我就被抛弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就只是个悲哀的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身上的皇室血脉 曾是她活着的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便生活贫困
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她依然梦想着 王室早晚会来接她的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果这个梦没能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈姆特的烈火轻而易举地要了她的命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲也被巴哈姆特的火球…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 讽刺的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因巴哈姆特一事 我被纳入了王室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字从妈妈取的克里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成了夏利欧斯17世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.10,0:12:58.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是住在贫民街的恶魔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就想去趟贫民街了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好 能带个路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带路？好…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对暴露了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他刚才说我是恶魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这雕刻有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个我买了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 这样不就暴露长相了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 去下个地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:31.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把头巾都取了 没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不妥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 我有很多问题想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看左上方墙上的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在监视你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.11,0:15:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甩掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算甩掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个手镯有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想问你点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.70,0:16:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身为国王 干了很多招神 招恶魔讨厌的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 化身为克里斯的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却对我很温柔 还跟我跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能笑着面对恶魔的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道哪张脸才是真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道你的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论付出多少代价
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须去完成某些事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是什么 我目前无法回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我的所作所为都是为了实现目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为国王 我做出了抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果就是现在这副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:37.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早已抛弃所谓的罪恶感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了质问自己的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.35,0:17:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去了愚蠢母亲的墓前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迄今为止 这份信念从未动摇过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 我唯独割舍不下你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不是你出现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我便能想往常一样 以王的身份活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不是遇见了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何想当个可怕的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想分担你背负的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以随时随地变身了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为接吻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见面要到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:20:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次是多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多久 多久
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次就是下次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:10.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 如果还有机会见面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会说出我的目标的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.50,0:21:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.37,0:23:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然早就被红龙迷惑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.71,0:23:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是亚纳提的凯撒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.38,0:23:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天界的贞德 你那边怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.55,0:23:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 这里是天界的贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.47,0:23:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我超闪耀 超耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.51,0:23:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 神击的巴哈姆特 Virgin Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:23:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永不言败
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.52,0:23:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德 请详细解说下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说很耀眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.56,0:24:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.65,0:24:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周也要看哦